snippet.title: Best VGM 1052 - Snowboard Kids 2 - Haunted House
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

N64
Snowboard Kids 2 (1999)
Haunted House
Tomohiko Sato, Isao Kasai & Sayuri Yamamoto
